data.description: Great listing to hit the market! Located in a prime location minutes away from local school, jobs, and restaurant's. Great size bedrooms and a restroom on each floor! Walkout basement allowing to get in out of the house whenever you need! Added insulation throughout the home and sealed all air leaks! Updated electrical panel and an added RV charging port! Gravel added for future RV parking! Replaced water heater, and replaced the backyard hose-bib. Storage shed with extra height to place any unused items for the season! Seller willing to contribute $5,000 towards closing cost closing cost or finishing the basement at buyer discretion! $450 towards carpet allowance  Ask about the Davis county grant program! Buyer/Buyer agent to verify all.
